<section class="how">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sec-head reveal"><span class="sec-index">04 / Process</span><span class="sec-rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="reveal">How we work</h2>
    <p class="sub reveal">From audit to agents doing the work, in weeks.</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="card glow-card reveal">
        <span class="ghost" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <h3>AI audit</h3>
        <p>We map how work actually moves through your business and find where hours are leaking. You get a ranked list of what to build first and what it's worth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card glow-card reveal">
        <span class="ghost" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <h3>Process redesign</h3>
        <p>We don't automate a broken process. We redesign the workflow around what agents do best and define exactly where humans stay in the loop.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card glow-card reveal">
        <span class="ghost" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <h3>Agent deployment</h3>
        <p>We build, train and deploy agents on your systems and your data. No migration off the tools you already use.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card glow-card reveal">
        <span class="ghost" aria-hidden="true">04</span>
        <h3>Compounding</h3>
        <p>Agents keep learning your business. Every week they run, the system gets sharper and the moat gets deeper. Your total time investment: a few hours, not a project team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
